cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DB, cs.PL, cs.DS

This paper deals with logical reasoning tasks, specifically Answer Set Programming (ASP), which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses temporal modalities and expiration control, which are related to the field of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO). The use of TMS for updating models of non-stratified programs is related to the field of Databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the use of Clingo, which is a solver for logic programs, and the use of incremental updates, which are related to the field of Programming Languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper deals with the evaluation of different reasoning mechanisms, which is related to the field of Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
